summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning amending Sections 23.45.006, 23.45.009, 23.45.014, 23.45.016, 23.45.048, 23.45.090, 23.45.146, 23.47.004, and 23.54.015 of Seattle Municipal Code, to add language inadvertently omitted and to correct errors in the adoption of recent legislation concerning child care and development standards for Multifamilly Structures, and declaring an emergency.
